   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,190:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The key insight: 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,193:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Vault is a storage and retrieval engine, not an AI itself.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,197:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  When you use it via MCP (which is the
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,198:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: recommended approach), Claude or whatever AI you
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,199:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,205:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: re chatting with handles the conversation, and Vault handles
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,207:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: the secure encrypted storage. When you use it standalone (CLI or web UI), Vault uses OpenAI/Ollama for the
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,208:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: conversational AI part.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,209:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Three Interfaces Explained
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,209:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 1. MCP Server (Recommended -- What We
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,210:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,210:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: re Using)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,211:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: What it is:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,217:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  MCP (Model Context Protocol) is a standard created by Anthropic that lets AI assistants use external
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,219:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: tools. Vault exposes itself as 17 MCP tools that any MCP-compatible AI can call.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: How it works in practice:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  You
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,221:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,222:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: re chatting with Claude in Cursor (like right now). You say 
