   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,223:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: type is O+
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,224:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,224:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . Claude sees it has a 
