   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,227:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,228:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  and value=
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,228:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,229:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: O+
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,229:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,231:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,231:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: and Vault encrypts and stores it in your local database. Later you ask 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,232:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,232:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: what
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,233:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,233:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s my blood type?
