   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,235:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  and Claude calls 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,236:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: vault_recall
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,236:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  to get the answer.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,237:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Why this is better:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,237:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  You don
