   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,243:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: re already using) becomes the
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 03:24:47,245:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: interface to your vault. The AI handles understanding what you want; Vault handles secure storage.
